title: Forlinx Embedded FET-D9360-C SoM Accommodates D9-Pro Processor and Up to 16GB RAM
description: In partnership with SemiDrive, Forlinx Embedded has introduced the FET-D9360-C System on Module (SoM), featuring the D9-Pro high-performance industrial processor. This SoM is designed for industrial applications demanding multi-display capabilities with resolutions up to 2K@60Hz.
